{"tid":1083020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又無得瞓覺？】傳RoadShow今年復播九巴電視廣告","createTime":"2019-03-29T10:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T04:21:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2afc62296538972866b179923ffb3f07a3235301","tid":1083020,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190329/large/1553848186_226e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F1553848186_226e.jpg&h=17e2076a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n載通（62）旗下九巴停止RoadShow廣告近2年後，有媒體引述知情人士稱，RoadShow將於今年在九巴復播，但未有時間表，4月時將有詳情公佈。<br />\n<br />\nRoadShow於2017年代理權到期後停播，網民歡呼一片，認為乘客終於不需再受到噪音騷擾。提供RoadShow節目的貝森金融（888，前稱路訊通）當時稱重整資源，集中資料投放於更有營利能力的業務。貝森金融主要業務範圍包括巴士車身廣告、車廂內部、候車亭及戶外廣告牌的銷售及設計。<br />\n<br />\n貝森金融股價今日跌2.54%，報1.15元。路訊通2018年賣殼予內地商人徐沛欣旗下貝森資本，並易名貝森金融。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190329/59426472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59426472&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7eNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=ac45c6d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F59426472&h=f8fb810f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190329/59426472</a>"},{"pid":"e8d70b1cd9edad35bef71840209979b3dd775144","tid":1083020,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a27467f42f5e3db7573bb8ad250ef33c25fcca34","tid":1083020,"uid":54516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:33:29.000Z","msg":"又瘋狂loop車淑梅了。"},{"pid":"fa24437d454bce6fbdaecb2dabf8942450747c0b","tid":1083020,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-